Adadin wadanda tsunami ya rutsa da su a Indonesia ya kai 832
Adadin wadanda suka mutu a girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta auku a Indonesia ya haura zuwa 832, a cewar hukumar kula da bala'i ta kasa da ta bayar da rahoto a safiyar yau Lahadi.
Mutane da yawa za su kasance cikin tarkacewar gine-ginen da girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta rushe a ranar Juma'a, wanda ya haifar da raƙuman ruwa masu tsayi har zuwa mita 6, in ji mai magana da yawun hukumar Sutopo Purwo Nugroho a wani taron manema labarai.
Garin Palu, da ke da mazauna fiye da 380,000, ya cika da fashewar gine-ginen da aka rushe.
'Yan sanda sun kama wani mutum mai shekaru 32 da laifin kisan kai bayan da wata mata ta mutu a hannun 'yan sanda.
An fara binciken kisan kai bayan da aka gano gawar wata mata a Birkenhead, Merseyside da safiyar yau.
An tsinci wata mata 'yar shekara 44 da rauni na wuka a karfe 7:55 na safe a kan titin John Street, inda aka kama wani mutum mai shekara 32 da ake zargi da kisan kai.
