Ba kasafai ake samun guguwar iska a Arizona ba, amma akwai yiwuwar a farkon mako mai zuwa, lokacin da ragowar guguwar Rosa ta yi wa'adi a hamada ta kudu maso yamma, da yiwuwar a samu ambaliyar ruwa.
Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Kasa ta ba da gargadin ambaliyar ruwa a ranar Litinin da Talata daga yammacin Arizona zuwa kudu maso gabashin Nevada, kudu maso gabashin California da Utah, gami da biranen Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City.
