López Obrador ya yi alkawarin ranar Asabar a dandalin Tlatelolco cewa ba zai sake amfani da sojoji don danne mutanen Mexico ba.
A ranar 2 ga Oktoba, 1968, sojojin sun yi ta harbi a kan wani zanga-zangar lumana a cikin dandalin, inda suka kashe mutane 300 a daidai lokacin da ƙungiyoyin ɗalibai ke ci gaba a duk Latin Amurka.
