A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Bincike na Artificial Intelligence wadda aka tsara don hada abokan hulda daga masana'antu da jami'a, kuma fadar White House ta sanar da kafa Kwamitin Bincike na Artificial Intelligence.
