Tambayar da aka gabatar a kuri'ar raba gardama ita ce: "Shin kana son shiga NATO da EU tare da amincewa da yarjejeniyar da Girka?
Masu goyon bayan sauya sunan, ciki har da Firaminista Zoran Zaev, sun yi zargin cewa ya zama farashin da ya dace a biya don samun damar shiga cikin ƙungiyoyi kamar EU ko NATO na Macedonia, ɗaya daga cikin ƙasashe masu tasowa daga faduwar Yugoslavia.
"Na zo nan yau don yin zabe don makomar kasar, don matasan Macedonia, don su iya rayuwa cikin 'yanci a karkashin kariyar Tarayyar Turai, saboda hakan yana nufin rayuwa mafi aminci ga dukkanmu", in ji Olivera Georgijevska, mai shekaru 79, a Skopje.
