HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton karuwar sabbin masu kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14 cikin 100
China ta ba da rahoton karuwar adadin mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV ko AIDS da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Ya shafi fiye da mutane 820,000 a kasar, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya.
An samu sabbin mutane 40,000 a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka ana samunsu ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ke nuna canji daga baya.
A dā, cutar HIV ta yadu da sauri a wasu ɓangarorin ƙasar Sin ta wurin ƙarin jini da aka yi da cutar.
Amma, adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ta HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma duk da haka, a shekara guda, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV ko AIDS a kasar Sin ya karu da 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta zama babbar matsala a tsakanin al'ummar kasar Sin masu luwadi da karuwanci.
A shekarar 1997, an haramta luwadi a China, amma sun ce nuna wariya ga 'yan luwadi ya yadu.
Saboda dabi'un da suka dace a kasar, bincike ya nuna cewa tsakanin kashi 70 zuwa 90 na maza da ke yin jima'i da maza za su yi aure.
Yawancin kamuwa da cutar ta zo ne daga rashin yin jima'i a cikin irin wannan dangantaka.
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da magani ga kowa a kasar Sin a matsayin wani ɓangare na kokarin magance cutar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani ma'aikacin ta ya tona bayanan 'yan majalisar dattijan na jam'iyyar Republican, "ƙarya mai haɗari" da kuma "ka'idojin ƙulla makirci"
A ranar Asabar, wakilin Amurka Maxine Waters, ta yi tir da zargin da ake yi cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya wallafa bayanan sirri na sanatocin Republican guda uku a shafukan 'yan majalisar na Wikipedia.
A wata sanarwa da wata 'yar jarida ta Los Angeles Democrat ta fitar, ta ce, shafukan yanar gizo da masu sharhi a kan shafukan yanar gizo na 'yan tsageru ne ke yin wannan furucin.
"Kakyawan karya, da kuma karin munanan karya", Waters ya yi tsokaci a cikin wata sanarwa a shafinsa na Twitter.
Rahoton ya ce, bayanan da aka fitar sun hada da adireshin gida da kuma lambobin waya na 'yan majalisar dattijai na Amurka Lindsey Graham na Carolina ta Kudu, da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, dukansu na Utah.
Bayanin ya bayyana a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani da ba a san shi ba ya wallafa a kan Capitol Hill, fadar gwamnatin Amurka, yayin da ake sauraron sauraron kotun majalisar dattijai game da zargin da ake yi na lalata da dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh.
Wannan ya faru ne jim kadan bayan da Sanatocin kasar uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ba da rahoton cewa adireshin IP da ke gano asalin abubuwan da aka buga yana da alaƙa da sashen Waters kuma sun bayyana bayanan daga ma'aikacin Waters, kamar yadda Capitol Hill ya ruwaito.
Waters ya ci gaba da cewa "Wannan zargi da ba shi da tushe, ƙarya ne gaba daya".
"Memba na ma'aikaci, wanda aka yi wa asirinsa, bayanansa da kuma tsaronsa zagon-kasa sakamakon wannan zargin na karya da zamba, ba shi da alhakin watsa wannan bayanin.
Wannan zargi da ba a ba da gaskiya ba, ƙarya ce kawai".
Bayanin Waters ya jawo suka a yanar gizo, ciki har da na tsohon Sakataren Fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙaryatãwa aka yi fushi", Fleischer rubuta.
"Ya nuna ba shi da halin zama dan Majalisa.
Idan aka zargi mutum da abin da bai yi ba, bai kamata ya yi fushi ba.
Bai kamata ya nuna cewa yana da ƙalubale ba.
Bai kamata ka yi shakkar dalilin da ya sa ake maka laifi ba.
Dole ne ya kasance cikin nutsuwa da kwanciyar hankali".
A cewar Fleischer, Waters ya yi daidai da yadda 'yan Democrat suka soki Alkalin Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukar suka ce ya yi fushi sosai a lokacin da ake sauraron shari'ar.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican da ya tsaya takarar maye gurbin Waters a zaben tsakiyar wa'adi, ya bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafin Twitter.
"Da ma ya kasance gaskiya", ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter.
A cikin sanarwa, Waters ya ce sashensa ya faɗakar da "masu bin doka da hukumomin da suka dace game da wannan zargin zamba.
"Za mu tabbatar da cewa mun gano wadanda suka aikata wannan", ya ci gaba, "kuma za mu tabbatar da cewa sun dauki alhakin aikata duk wani abu da ya shafi halaka da kuma hadari ga kowane daya daga cikin mambobin tawagar".
Binciken Johnny English Strikes Again (Johnny English: Sake a cikin Aiki), Rowan Atkinson na ɗan leƙen asirin ba da izinin ba
Ya zama al'ada don neman fifikon Brexit a cikin sabbin fina-finai daga ra'ayi na Burtaniya kuma da alama wannan na iya amfani da dawowar wannan jerin wasan kwaikwayo da wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English, wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya dawo rayuwa a 2011 tare da Johnny English Reborn (Johnny English Returns).
Shin za a iya yin amfani da wannan ba'a game da yadda muke da wauta a cikin sabuwar damar da aka fitar da ita?
Ko ta yaya, Johnny English, mai fuska mai ban tsoro, mai fuska mai ban tsoro, ya sake ba da lasisinsa don ɓata abubuwa a karo na biyu.
Hakika, shi ne wawayar 'yar sandan da, duk da cewa tana da'awar cewa tana da kwarjini, ta na da ɗan Clouseau, da ɗan Mr. Bean, da kuma ɗan irin wannan mutumin da ya ba da gudummawa a cikin waƙa guda ɗaya a kan taken Wasan Wuta a lokacin bikin buɗe wasannin Olympics na London na 2012.
Hakanan asalinsa ya dogara ne akan ɗan jarida na duniya da asirin ƙasa da ƙasa wanda Atkinson ya taɓa yin wasa a cikin tallan talabijin na Barclaycard da aka manta da su yanzu, wanda ya haifar da hargitsi a cikin hanyarsa.
Akwai wasu abubuwa masu kyau a cikin wasan karshe da Johnny English ya yi.
Ina son lokacin da Johnny English ya kusanci wani jirgi mai saukar ungulu yayin da yake sanye da kayan yaƙi na ƙarni na farko kuma ƙafafun rotor ɗin ya yi ɗan ƙaramin ƙarfi a kan kwalkwali.
Atkinson yana da kyauta ga wasan kwaikwayo na jiki yana da kyau, amma yana ba da ra'ayi cewa ba'a da karfi kuma ba shi da amfani, musamman ma lokacin da irin wannan fim din "mai tsanani", kamar 007 da kuma Ofishin Jakadancin, sun riga sun yi amfani da wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin daya daga cikin abubuwan da suke ciki.
Kamar dai an yi wa yara ba'a, maimakon manya, kuma a ganina, ba'a da Johnny English ba ne mai ban mamaki ba kamar yadda Atkinson yayi a cikin fim din fim din lokacin da yake nunawa Bean.
Yanzu dai, hujja da aka yi a kai, ita ce, Birtaniya na da matsala mai tsanani.
Wani ɗan fashin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin cibiyar leken asiri na Burtaniya kuma ya fallasa sunayen duk wani ɗan sandan Burtaniya da ke yankin, abin da ya sa baƙin cikin wannan ɗan sandan da ke kan aiki, ya zama ɗan ƙaramin abin da ya faru ga Kevin Eldon.
Wannan shi ne babban abin da ya kamata a yi wa wata firaminista mai cike da rikici, wadda ta riga ta fuskanci matsalar rashin farin jini a siyasar kasar: Emma Thompson ta yi iya kokarinta a wannan hali da kusan ya yi kama da Theresa May, amma ba za a iya yin wani abu mai yawa da rubutun ba.
Masu ba shi shawara sun gaya masa cewa tun da dukan 'yan leƙen asirin da suke aiki a wannan yankin sun yi alkawari, zai bukaci ya zaɓi wani da ya riga ya yi ritaya.
Wannan yana nufin Johnny English mai rashin hankali a cikin mutum, wanda yanzu yake aiki a matsayin malami a wasu cibiyoyin snob, amma yana ba da darussan ba bisa ƙa'ida ba game da yadda ake zama wakili mai ɓoye; a cikin wannan ɓangaren akwai wasu barkwanci, lokacin da English ya ba da makarantar leken asiri ga makarantar dutsen.
An dawo da Ingilishi zuwa Whitehall don taron gaggawa na gaggawa kuma ya haɗu da tsohon abokin aikinsa Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake bugawa.
Bough yanzu ya zama mutum mai aure da kuma kyaftin jirgin ruwa, wani abu da yake son yi wanda Vicki Pepperdine ta rasa.
A nan ne Batman da Robin suka sake komawa cikin aikin da suka yi a ofishin Sirrin Sarauniya, inda suka hadu da mace mai ban mamaki Ophelia Bulletova.
A halin da ake ciki, Firaminista tana cikin haɗari saboda sha'awar mai son fasaha wanda ya yi ikirarin zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Biritaniya: Jason Volta, wanda Jake Lacy ya yi.
Turanci da Bough sun fara aikin su na rashin hankali: sun yi kama da masu hidima, sun ƙone wani gidan cin abinci na Faransa; sun haifar da tashin hankali wanda ya sa suka shiga jirgin ruwa na Volta; kuma Turanci ya haifar da cikakken rikici yayin da suke ƙoƙarin amfani da kwalliyar VR don sanin gida na Volta.
Tabbas, duk an kama su ne a wannan jerin na karshe, amma a cikin kyakkyawar hanyar da take, da kuma yadda take da ban haushi, kamar dai ta fito ne daga wani shirin TV na yara.
