Amurka za ta iya amfani da sojojin ruwanta wajen aiwatar da "shinge" don hana Rasha fitar da makamashin, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka
"Idan ya zama dole", Washington na iya amfani da ruwan teku don hana makamashin Rasha shiga kasuwannin, ciki har da na Gabas ta Tsakiya, ya bayyana Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka, Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda aka ruwaito a cikin Washington Examiner.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa, shiga tsakani da Rasha ke yi a Syria, musamman inda take aiki a karkashin umarnin gwamnati mai ci, wani dalili ne na neman sabbin kasuwanni na makamashi.
"Ina ganin dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne suna son yin kasuwanci da makamashin kamar yadda suka yi a Gabashin Turai", in ji shi, kamar yadda aka ruwaito.
Ƙari ga haka, a cewar ma'aikacin, suna da hanyoyin da za su magance matsalar.
"Amurka tana da iko, tare da rundunar sojan ruwa, don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa suna bude kuma, idan ya zama dole, toshe su don tabbatar da makamashin su ba ya zuwa kasuwa", in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi wannan jawabi ne ga masu halartar taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta da ke kiran kanta a matsayin "muryar masu amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya kwatanta dabarun Washington na magance Rasha da Iran, yana mai cewa, a aikace, wannan abu ɗaya ne.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki a Iran da Rasha ya ƙunshi, fiye ko ƙasa da haka, don amfani da maye gurbin mai", in ji shi, yayin da yake magana game da Rasha yana cewa "kawai yana da dabara" tare da tattalin arzikin da ke dogara da hydrocarbons.
An yi wannan magana ne yayin da gwamnatin Trump ke kan manufa ta bunkasa fitar da iskar gas din kasar zuwa Turai, don maye gurbin na Rasha, wanda shi ne mafi arha ga masu amfani da gas a Turai.
Don haka, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban kasar kansa, sun yi kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga "rashin dacewar" aikin bututun mai na Nord Stream 2, wanda, a cewar Trump, ya mai da Berlin "bauta" ga Moscow.
Moscow ta yi ta nanata cewa aikin famfon mai na dala biliyan 11 na Nord Stream 2 wanda aka tsara don ninka karfin da ake da shi na famfon mai zuwa mita miliyan 110 na mai, ba wani aikin tattalin arziki ba ne kawai.
Fadar Kremlin ta yi jayayya cewa tsananin adawar Washington ga aikin ya kasance ne kawai saboda dalilai na tattalin arziki kuma misali ne na gasa mara kyau.
"Ina ganin mun yarda da cewa ba za a yi amfani da makamashi a matsayin wata hanyar yin amfani da karfi ba, kuma masu amfani da shi ya kamata su iya zabar masu samar da shi", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha, Aleksandr Novak, bayan ganawa da Sakataren Makamashi na Amurka, Rick Perry, a watan Satumba a Moscow.
Wannan matakin da Amurka ta dauka ya sa Jamus ta sake jaddada aniyarta na ci gaba da wannan aikin.
Ƙungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus BDI, wadda ita ce babbar ƙungiya a wannan fannin, ta yi kira ga Amurka da ta janye daga manufofin makamashi na EU da kuma yarjejeniyar makamashi tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala idan wata kasa ta uku ta shiga tsakaninmu da samar da makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban BDI, bayan wani taro da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin Angela Merkel, shugabar gwamnatin Jamus, da kuma Vladimir Putin, shugaban Rasha.
Elizabeth Warren za ta duba sosai kan takarar shugabancin kasa a 2020, in ji 'yar majalisar dattijai ta Massachusetts
A ranar Asabar, 'yar majalisar dattijai daga jihar Massachusetts Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta yi duba sosai kan ko za ta yi takarar shugabancin kasa bayan zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar shekara.
A lokacin wani taron jama'a a Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ya tabbatar da cewa zai yi la'akari da takararsa.
"Lokaci ya yi da ya kamata mata su je Washington su gyara gwamnatin da ta lalace kuma wannan ya hada da mace a kan mulki", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
"Bayan Ranar 6 ga Nuwamba, zan yi tunani sosai game da takarar shugabancin kasa".
Warren ya yi tsokaci game da Shugaba Donald Trump a yayin taron jama'a, yana mai cewa yana "kai wannan kasar zuwa inda ba ta dace ba.
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ta fito fili wajen sukar Trump da kuma dan takararsa na Kotun Koli, Brett Kavanaugh.
A ranar Juma'a, Warren ya yi tsokaci a shafinsa na Twitter cewa "hakika ana bukatar binciken FBI kafin a jefa kuri'a".
