Mickelson, wanda ke halartar taron shekara-shekara na 12 a karo na 12, ya kasance a kan kujera ta hanyar yanke shawara na Kyaftin Jim Furyk kuma ba zai iya shiga cikin wasan kwallon hudu ba ko kuma a ranar Asabar.
Maimakon kasancewa a tsakiyar wasan, kamar yadda ya faru da Amurka sau da yawa, zakara mai sau biyar ya ciyar da ranar yana ta'aziyya da kuma aiki don inganta motsinsa.
