Kamar kowa, tana son ta kasance a waje".
A ranar Lahadin nan, Mickelson zai zarce Nick Faldo a matsayin wanda ya fi kowa yawan wasanni a gasar Ryder Cup.
Zai iya kawo ƙarshen aikinsa a Ryder Cup, wanda bai taɓa kaiwa matsayin sa na mutum ba.
Mickelson yana da nasara 18, rashin nasara 20, da rabi bakwai, duk da cewa Furyk ya ce kasancewarsa yana ba da kayan aiki ga ƙungiyar.
"Shi mutum ne mai ban dariya, mai ban dariya, mai dabara kuma yana son yin rikici da mutane, yana da kyau a samu a cikin tawagar", in ji shi.
