Eilidh Doyle za ta zama "muryar 'yan wasa" a kwamitin hukumar wasannin motsa jiki na Scotland
An zabi Eilidh Doyle a cikin hukumar hukumar 'yan wasa ta Scotland a matsayin darakta mai zaman kanta a babban taron shekara-shekara na kwamitin gudanarwa.
Doyle ita ce 'yar wasan Scotland mafi samun lambar yabo kuma Shugaba Ian Beattie ya bayyana wannan a matsayin babbar dama ga wadanda ke jagorantar wasan don cin gajiyar kwarewar ta a matakin kasa da kasa a cikin shekaru goma da suka gabata.
"Eilidh tana da mutunci sosai a cikin al'ummar Scotland, da Burtaniya da kuma duniya baki daya, kuma muna da tabbacin cewa wasannin motsa jiki na Scotland zai amfana sosai daga kasancewa a kan kwamitin", in ji Beattie.
