Ba'amurkar, wacce ta lashe tseren mita 200 da mita 400 a wasannin Atlanta na 1996 tsakanin jimillar zinare hudu na gasar Olympics kuma a yanzu tana aiki a matsayin mai sharhi na yau da kullun ga BBC, ta kamu da ciwon shan wahala wanda ya hana ta tafiya.
