Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, ta yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane akalla 384, in ji majiyar hukuma, kuma ana sa ran adadin zai karu.
Saboda katsewar sadarwa, ba a sami bayanai daga yankin Donggala ba, yankin da ke arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai girman 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Celebes:
Palu babban birni ne na lardin Celebes ta Tsakiya, wanda ke ƙarshen ƙofar ƙofar bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Celebes, wanda ke da mazaunan kusan 379,800 a cikin 2017.
Garin ya yi bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka auku.
Donggala wani yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Celebes.
Wannan yankin, wani yanki ne na gwamnati ƙasa da lardi, yana da yawan jama'a kusan 299,200 a shekara ta 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan ginshiƙan tattalin arziƙin lardin Central Sulawesi, musamman a yankin Donggala na gabar teku.
Ma'adinai na nickel suna da mahimmanci a lardin, amma sun fi mayar da hankali ne a Morowali, a gefen gabar Celebes.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata a cewar Hukumar Gudanar da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekarar 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya kuma shafi yammacin Donggala a 1996, inda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane tara.
Indonesia tana kan Zirin Wuta na Pacific na babban aikin girgizar ƙasa, saboda haka tana fuskantar girgizar ƙasa akai-akai.
Waɗannan su ne manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wani babban girgizar kasa a gabar tekun yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia, a arewacin Sumatra, wanda ya faru a ranar 26 ga Disamba, ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14, wanda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin, a Aceh.
2005: An samu girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin Sumatra a karshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, inda ta haifar da tsunami da ta lalata gabar tekun kudu, inda ta kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: An samu girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.6 a kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, wanda ke gab da Sumatra, inda ta haifar da tsunami mai girman mita 10 wanda ya lalata dubun-dubatar ƙauyuka kuma ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar kusan mutane 300.
2016: Wata mummunar girgizar kasa ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya da ke Aceh, inda ta haifar da lalacewa da kuma fargaba, yayin da mutane suka tuna da bala'in da aka yi a 2004 da ya yi sanadiyar girgizar kasa da tsunami.
A wannan karon babu tsunami, amma fiye da mutane 100 sun mutu saboda rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Manyan girgizar ƙasa sun faru a tsibirin Lombok na Indonesiya, inda mutane sama da 500 suka mutu, yawancinsu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar kasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a cikin wani yanayi na ɗan lokaci.
An kama ɗan fari na Sarah Palin da laifin cin zarafin iyali
