Tarayya masu gabatar da kara suna neman aiwatar da hukuncin kisa da aka saba aukuwa ga wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a birnin New York suna neman a yankewa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da laifin kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas, hukuncin da ba a yanke ba a jihar tun a shekara ta 1953.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, an yi zargin ya yi amfani da wata motar haya daga Home Depot don kai hari a kan titin keke a kan Babbar Hanyar West Side a Lower Manhattan, inda ya ci gaba da bin diddigin rayuwar masu tafiya da ƙafa da ke kan hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don bayar da hujjar hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su nuna cewa Saipov ya "da gangan" ya kashe mutane takwas da aka kashe kuma ya yi musu mummunan rauni "da gangan", a cewar sanarwar da aka gabatar game da neman hukuncin kisa a Kudancin Gundumar New York.
Dukansu laifuffukan na da hukuncin kisa bisa ga takardar da kotun ta rubuta.
Bayan makonni bayan harin, wani babban alkalin kotun tarayya ya tuhumi Saipov da aikata laifuka 22, ciki har da kisan kai guda takwas a cikin haɗin gwiwa tare da wata ƙungiya ta aikata laifuka, al'ada da ake amfani da ita a cikin shari'o'in aikata laifuka, da kuma aikata laifuka guda na tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "tsarin tunani da kuma shiri mai kyau", in ji masu sauraron shari'a yayin da suke bayyana yadda Saipov ya aiwatar da "mummunan, mugun kuma lalataccen" harin.
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya jawo rauni, lalacewa da asara ga iyalai da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco" kamar yadda aka bayyana a cikin sanarwar da ake son tuhuma.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga kasar Argentina.
Gundumar Kudancin New York ba ta yi shari'ar kisa ba a cikin shekaru goma.
An samu wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da laifin kashe wasu 'yan kasuwa biyu masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi, amma daga bisani an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A karshe da aka yi amfani da hukuncin kisa a wani shari'ar tarayya a New York a 1953, a cikin shari'ar Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'auratan da aka kashe bayan da aka yanke musu hukuncin kisa kan aikata leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenbergs a cikin kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, haifaffen Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin nadama a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin kamar yadda takardun kotu suka nuna.
Ya shaida wa masu bincike cewa ya ji daɗi da abin da ya yi, in ji 'yan sanda.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa yin wannan harin ya samo asali ne daga bidiyon ISIS da ake zargi ya kalli a wayar sa.
Ya kuma nemi izinin ganin tutar ISIS a cikin ɗakinsa na asibiti, in ji 'yan sanda.
An same shi da laifin aikata laifi 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin da aka ba wa izini na tarayya da aka ba da izini don wakiltar Saipov, ya nuna cewa suna "bayyane ba su da farin ciki" da hukuncin da ake tuhumar.
"Muna da tabbacin cewa hukuncin da aka yanke na neman a yanke masa hukuncin kisa maimakon a yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai ba tare da wani dalili na sokewa ba zai kara wahalhal da wannan lamarin ya jawo wa duk wanda ya shafa", in ji Patton.
Tawagar kare Saipov ta nemi masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi a yanke masa hukuncin kisa.
