Dan takarar Tory, kuma mai goyon bayan Brexit Andrea Jenkyns, ita ma ta halarci taron, inda ta yi wa manema labarai bayani: "Abin da kawai nake cewa shi ne: Firaminista, ku saurari jama'a.
