Ta yaya yakin kasuwanci tsakanin Amurka da China zai iya zama mai kyau ga Beijing
Farkon fashewar bam din da Amurka ta yi a yakin cinikayya da China ya yi matukar jan hankali, kuma duk da cewa yakin bai kare ba, amma yin sulhu tsakanin kasashen biyu zai iya amfanar da Beijing a dogon lokaci, in ji masana.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya ba da gargadi na farko a farkon wannan shekarar, inda ya yi wa manyan kayayyakin da kasar Sin ke fitarwa haraji, da suka hada da bangarorin hasken rana, da karafa da kuma aluminum.
Babban tashin hankali ya zo ne a wannan makon tare da sanya sabbin haraji da suka shafi kwatankwacin dala biliyan 200, da ke ɗaukar rabin kayayyakin da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
Kasar Sin ta yi ta kai hare-hare a kan irin wadannan kayayyaki, a baya-bayan nan ta kara harajin da ta sanya kan kayayyakin Amurka da suka kai dala biliyan 60 daga kashi biyar zuwa goma.
China ta yi alkawarin yin koyi da Amurka, kuma ba za a yi tsammanin tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu ya yi kasa a wani lokaci ba.
Don samun Washington ta koma baya, zai zama dole a yi biyayya ga bukatunsu, amma yin biyayya ga Amurka a bainar jama'a zai zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Amma duk da haka, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi amfani da takardun ta yadda ya kamata, to, matsin lamba na yakin kasuwanci da Amurka zai iya taimaka wa China a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro da tattalin arzikin biyu.
"Gaskiyar cewa wani mataki na siyasa a Washington ko Beijing na iya haifar da yanayin da ake bukata don fara rikicin tattalin arziki a kasashen biyu ya kasance da gaske ya fi hatsari fiye da yadda aka sani a baya", in ji Abigail Grace, mai bincike na Asiya a Cibiyar Nazarin Sabon Tsaro na Amurka.
Syria ta shirya don 'yan gudun hijira su dawo, in ji Ministan Harkokin Waje
Syria ta ce a shirye take ta dawo da 'yan gudun hijirar da yardar rai, kuma tana neman taimako don sake gina kasar da ta shafe shekaru bakwai ana yaki.
A jawabinsa ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan harkokin waje Walid al-Moualem ya ce yanayin kasar na samun sauki.
"Yanzu haka al'amuran da ke faruwa a kasar sun fi zaman lafiya da kwanciyar hankali saboda ci gaban da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gyaran guraren da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata domin dawo da al'amuran da suka saba.
Yanzu an samar da dukkan yanayin da ake bukata don dawowar 'yan gudun hijira da son rai zuwa kasar da suka bar saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki na gefe daya da suka shafi rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa fiye da 'yan Siriya miliyan 5.5 sun tsere daga kasar tun bayan barkewar yakin a shekarar 2011.
Sauran mutane miliyan shida na ci gaba da zama a kasar kuma suna bukatar taimakon jinkai.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Siriya za ta yi godiya da duk wani taimako da za ta samu don sake gina kasar da ta lalace.
Amma ya ce ba zai amince da wani taimako ba ko kuma daga kasashen da suka goyi bayan juyin mulkin ba.
Turai ta yi nasara a gasar cin kofin Ryder a Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018 ta hanyar doke kungiyar Amurka da maki na karshe na 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National Club da ke kusa da Paris, Faransa.
Wannan shi ne karo na shida a jere da Amurka ta yi rashin nasara a Turai kuma ta kasance ba ta lashe kofin Ryder a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe gasar ne a lokacin da tawagar Danish Thomas Bjorn ta kai maki 14.5 da take bukata don doke Amurka.
Tauraron dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya fi yawan fadace-fadace a gasar, ya jefa kwallo a cikin ruwa a rami 16 na par 3, ya rasa wasan da ya yi da Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan na Italiya ya haskaka a duk wasannin da ya buga, ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu da suka ci 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Ba'amurke Jordan Spieth ya ci nasara 5&4 da dan wasan Turai mafi muni Thorbjorn Olesen daga Denmark.
Dustin Johnson, wanda ya kasance a saman duniya, ya yi rashin nasara a wasan da ya buga da dan wasan Ingila Ian Poulter, wanda zai iya buga gasar Ryder Cup a karshe.
Tsohon dan wasa da ya lashe gasar Ryder Cup takwas, dan Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama dan wasan Turai da ya fi samun nasara a gasar, tare da maki 25.5.
